Only GL 4. Stay away from anything that mentions anything else along with 4.
Stay away from 5.
Here is the Redline site:
http://www.redlineoil.com/whyredline.htm
Scroll down to Product Application. Then down to MTL and MT90.
MTL is GL 4 in 70W80 weight.
MT90 is GL 4 in 75W90 weight.


